" F5                start/continue debugging
" Shift F5          stop debugging
" Ctrl+Shift F5     restart debugging
" F6                Pause
" F9                Toggle breakpoint on current line
" Shift F9          Add a function breakpoint for the expression under the cursor
" F10               Step over
